17 §1863. Bayou Growth Opportunity Workforce Program; creation; awards for
18 workforce training; application criteria
19 A. The purpose of the Bayou Growth Opportunity Workforce Program
20 herein referred to as "the program" is to provide competitive awards to qualified
21 employers for workforce training, including but not limited to talent enhancement,
22 increasing worker productivity, development of worker skills, leadership and
23 management training, and worker retention.
24 B. The department shall operate the program and coordinate the
25 implementation of the program with workforce development boards. The
26 department and the workforce development boards shall conduct outreach to inform
27 employers about the program.
28 C.(1) Upon the request of a qualified employer, a workforce development
29 board staff member shall conduct an evaluation with the employer to determine
